cs.IT, cs.NI, cs.SY, cs.MM, cs.MA

This paper deals with the measurement and analysis of 3D MIMO channels, which falls under the domain of information theory (cs.IT) and networked systems (cs.NI). The paper also presents a low-cost test equipment and post-processing algorithms, which could be categorized under systems and control (cs.SY). The use of massive MIMO and beamforming techniques in 3D MIMO systems could also be related to multimedia (cs.MM) and machine learning (cs.MA) sub-categories.
